data.description: This 2 Bedroom, 2 Full Bath, Cape Cod could easily be converted to a 3 or 4 bedroom home. The living room and bedrooms have hardwood flooring, and the eat-in, 32 handle kitchen features newer stainless steel appliances. The walkout lower level family room  (not included in square footage) provides additional living space and there is still plenty of room for storage. Other features include a covered rear patio, new roof, new front and back doors, natural gas heat, central a/c, maintenance free brick exterior, storage shed, nice lot, driveway cut in, within walking distance to Muhlenberg High School.
